<codeline><highlight class="normal">@details<sp/>This<sp/>namespace<sp/>provides<sp/>core<sp/>data<sp/>structures<sp/>for<sp/>managing<sp/>GameObjects,<sp/>including<sp/>object<sp/>pools<sp/>for<sp/>memory-efficient<sp/>entity<sp/>recycling<sp/>(GameObjectPool,<sp/>GameObjectPoolId,<sp/>GameObjectPoolRegistry),<sp/>filtered<sp/>views<sp/>for<sp/>querying<sp/>entities<sp/>based<sp/>on<sp/>state<sp/>or<sp/>components<sp/>(GameObjectFilter,<sp/>GameObjectView).<sp/>For<sp/>coordinated<sp/>pool/world<sp/>operations,<sp/>see<sp/>GameObjectPoolFacade.</highlight></codeline>
